    <div class="container" style="padding-top: 3%;">
        <h1 style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 4%;">Contact</h1>
        <p>For setup procedure, Kindly visit <a href="https://github.com/SachinVekariya" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            Page.</p>
